verses.text_plain: In Judah is God known: his name is great in Israel.
verses.verse_html:
1In Judah is God known: his name is great in Israel. ▼
▼ chief…: or, overseer
 , ▼
▼ of: or, for

verses.text_plain: In Salem also is his tabernacle, and his dwelling place in Zion.
verses.verse_html: 2In Salem also is his tabernacle, and his dwelling place in Zion.

verses.text_plain: There brake he the arrows of the bow, the shield, and the sword, and the battle. Selah.
verses.verse_html: 3There brake he the arrows of the bow, the shield, and the sword, and the battle. Selah.

verses.text_plain: Thou art more glorious and excellent than the mountains of prey.
verses.verse_html: 4Thou art more glorious and excellent than the mountains of prey.

verses.text_plain: The stouthearted are spoiled, they have slept their sleep: and none of the men of might have found their hands.
verses.verse_html: 5The stouthearted are spoiled, they have slept their sleep: and none of the men of might have found their hands.

verses.text_plain: At thy rebuke, O God of Jacob, both the chariot and horse are cast into a dead sleep.
verses.verse_html: 6At thy rebuke, O God of Jacob, both the chariot and horse are cast into a dead sleep.

tokens.text: are cast into a dead sleep

verses.text_plain: Thou, even thou, art to be feared: and who may stand in thy sight when once thou art angry?
verses.verse_html: 7Thou, even thou, art to be feared: and who may stand in thy sight when once thou art angry?

verses.text_plain: Thou didst cause judgment to be heard from heaven; the earth feared, and was still,
verses.verse_html: 8Thou didst cause judgment to be heard from heaven; the earth feared, and was still,

verses.text_plain: When God arose to judgment, to save all the meek of the earth. Selah.
verses.verse_html: 9When God arose to judgment, to save all the meek of the earth. Selah.

verses.text_plain: Surely the wrath of man shall praise thee: the remainder of wrath shalt thou restrain.
verses.verse_html: 10Surely the wrath of man shall praise thee: the remainder of wrath shalt thou restrain.

verses.text_plain: Vow, and pay unto the Lord your God: let all that be round about him bring presents unto him that ought to be feared.
verses.verse_html:
11Vow, and pay unto the Lord your God: let all that be round about him bring presents unto him that ought to be feared. ▼
▼ unto him…: Heb. to fear

tokens.text: let all that be round about
unto him that ought to be feared

footnotes.body_html: ▼ unto him…: Heb. to fear

verses.text_plain: He shall cut off the spirit of princes: he is terrible to the kings of the earth.
verses.verse_html: 12He shall cut off the spirit of princes: he is terrible to the kings of the earth.
